{
  "texts": [
    "-Goal-Given a text document with a preliminary list of potential entities, verify, and identify all entities of the specified types within the text.",
    "Note that the initial list may contain missing or incorrect entities.",
    "Additionally, determine and label the relationships among the verified entities.",
    "-Entity Types-A project refers to the scientific program, field campaign, or project from which the data were collected.",
    "A location is a place on Earth, a location within Earth, a vertical location, or a location outside of the Earth."
  ]
}